    • resolved

      protected boolean resolved
      flag indicating whether node resolution has occurred (if true, can just use first and only result in outgoing). Note that if flag has been set to resolved, the single outgoing connection may hold a value that it is not directly connected too, but is the representative of its contiguous group.
